donations.donation_comment: My hubby and I pray for you daily! He is very sick therefore we cannot join in protesting so we thank you from the bottom of our hearts. God bless you and keep you.

You guys are heroes! You are changing the whole world! Thank you for saving us ALL from the fascist One World Order! These vaccines and mask mandates were NEVER about our health and were always about controlling us, attacking Christians and depopulation of the world. The police MUST stand WITH you, not against you! History will remember the sides we ALL take! Stay UNITED! With Love from Florida!

Dear Truckers and Freedom Fighters,   
You are opening up the heart of our world.  Thank you thank you thank you for giving us hope, for showing us  the freedom to express, for giving us a path to choose,  for standing strong.    I send love, praise, gratitude, hope and trust.

I applaud the Canadian truckers taking a stand against government oppression, and that governments attempt to force an experimental lethal injection on their own people. This stand against tyranny knows no boundaries. This whole COVID mess is about money, and the Bible says it best in 1Tim 6:10.

US citizens and Christians support our neighbors to the north!
Keep fighting the good fight truckers!
